ed check or deposit slip  You may also sign up for the Commonwealth s REDI VIRGINIA EDI notification system  Follow the directions to sign up and you can elect to be notified by email when your reimbursement is being deposited  Travel EDI Enrollment Form Instructions to enroll in REDI VIRGINIA If you have questions regarding this program please contact the Institute s EDI Coordinator  Travel Office Travel Travel EDI Direct Deposit Travel Forms Travel FAQs VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 